  "commit_message": "Salt the FOD in tests/functional/dependencies.nix too\n\nWe want the outPath to be different between tests as well, not just\nthe drvPath. Existing hashInvalidator is for use in the same test -\nnot between different ones. Also it invalidates only the FOD's drvPath,\nwhich doesn't change the final outPath due to hash modulo.\n\nThis should additionally improve test isolation for tests with a shared store.",
